---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Free AI Search Audits Compared 2026 | Rank4AI" description="Comparison of free AI search audit tools and services. Which free audits are worth using and what do they actually test.">
<section class="pt-12 pb-24 reveal">
  <div class="container-narrow">
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Research', href: '/research/' },
      { label: 'Rankings', href: '/research/rankings/' },
      { label: 'Free Ai Search Audits' }
    ]} />

    <p class="section-tag">Rankings</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Free AI Search Audits Compared</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/stat-77-percent.svg" alt="UK AI visibility research data" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">Several agencies and tools now offer free AI search audits. But they vary enormously in what they actually test. Some check a single platform with a handful of prompts. Others test all six major AI platforms across five signal layers.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-5">This comparison helps you understand what you are getting from each free audit and which ones deliver genuine insight versus surface-level metrics.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-12 mb-4">What to Look For in a Free AI Audit</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">How many platforms?</span> – a free audit that only checks ChatGPT tells you 1/6 of the picture.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Automated or manual?</span> – automated tools give quick scores. Manual audits give context and recommendations.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Do they show competitor data?</span> – knowing where you stand means nothing without knowing where competitors stand.</p></div>
      <div class="card-teal-border"><p class="text-sm text-text-muted"><span class="highlight">Actionable or just a score?</span> – a number without a plan is not useful.</p></div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <!-- Internal links -->
    <div class="mt-12 pt-8 border-t border-border">
      <h2 class="!text-xl mb-4">Related</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3">
                <a href="/research/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">All Research</span></a>
        <a href="/research/uk-ai-visibility-stats/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">UK AI Statistics</span></a>
        <a href="/research/methodology/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-teal group-hover:text-accent">Our Methodology</span></a>
        <a href="/free-audit/" class="card group text-sm"><span class="font-medium text-accent">Get a Free Audit &rarr;</span></a>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="bg-off-white border-t border-border text-center py-16 px-10 mt-16">
    <h2 class="!text-2xl mb-4">Get a real AI search audit – free</h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted mb-8 max-w-[400px] mx-auto text-sm">All six platforms. All five signal layers. Competitor analysis included. No obligation.</p>
    <a href="/free-audit/" class="cta-primary">Get a Free AI Search Visibility Audit &rarr;</a>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
